snippet.title: Bomb Rush Cyberfunk - Official Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Bomb Rush Cyberfunk is coming out on Steam & Nintendo Switch at 18 Augustus 2023. 

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1353230/Bomb_Rush_Cyberfunk/

Wishlist on the Nintendo eShop: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/bomb-rush-cyberfunk-switch/

Footage from this trailer has been captured on a Nintendo Switch 

The game will be available at other platforms at a later date.

music: kidkanevil - Big City Life ft OV (written by G. Roberts and P. Mukhi)
